-- Vale Wants Thyssen Mill Stake in Brazil, WirtschaftsWoche Says
-- B y   J o s e   S e r g i o   O s s e
-- 2012-06-02T17:58:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-02/vale-wants-thyssen-mill-stake-in-brazil-wirtschaftswoche-says.html
Vale SA (VALE5)  is interested in buying out
 ThyssenKrupp AG (TKA) ’s stake in a steel mill both companies run as a
joint venture in Brazil, the German magazine WirtschafsWoche
reported, citing unidentified people at Vale.  Vale owns 27 percent of the mill, located at Sepetiba Bay
in Brazil’s Rio de Janeiro state, according to the magazine. The
article contained no other details.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jose Sergio Osse in  Sao Paulo  at 
 josse1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sylvia Wier at   swier@bloomberg.net  